Subject: Adult Swim Drop-In (18+ Years) | Jim Archdekin 9:30-10:30am
Description: Open to participants 18 years of age or older of all swimming abilities.  Facility Swim Test can be enforced by lifeguards to participants if weak swimming ability is present.
RegistrationNotes: Aquatic Admission Standards: All swim participants five (5) years of age or younger must be directly supervised by a parent/guardian who is at least fourteen (14) years of age. The parent/guardian must be in the water wearing bathing attire, within arm's reach of the swimmer, and able to render immediate assistance if necessary.
